{"id":608421,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/04/【网络民议】今年的海报像树上吊死了个那谁/","date":"2019-04-02T10:16:36Z","modified":"2019-04-02T10:19:32Z","title":"【网络民议】今年的海报像树上吊死了个那谁","content":"<blockquote><p><strong>看资讯 | 2019北京国际电影节海报揭晓 设计遭吐槽</strong></p>\n<p>2019年第九届北京国际电影节的海报于4月2日公布，其设计遭到了不少网友的吐槽。这到底是什么样的海报设计呢？</p>\n<p>海报以女神形态的奖杯为中心，蓝天背景，绿树占据了海报上方很大的位置。相关说明对该海报进行了解读。文章称，天坛女神/屹立苍穹/脚踏大地/播洒芬芳于参天之树/振臂向天/唤醒晨光于璀璨星空……寓意万物并生、传承七十载中国影人家国情怀。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-608424\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/04/699132e6gy1g1o88pnvukj20ku0vdnaq.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"662\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/04/699132e6gy1g1o88pnvukj20ku0vdnaq.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/04/699132e6gy1g1o88pnvukj20ku0vdnaq-199x300.jpg 199w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-608435\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/04/592c38a3ly1g1obpd2dvtj20v91von4g.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"953\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/04/592c38a3ly1g1obpd2dvtj20v91von4g.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/04/592c38a3ly1g1obpd2dvtj20v91von4g-139x300.jpg 139w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>以下为中国数字时代编辑辑自网络：</strong></p>\n<p>@豆瓣电影：2011至2019，历届北京国际电影节海报一览。</p>\n\n\t\t<style type='text/css'>\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 {\n\t\t\t\tmargin: auto;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-item {\n\t\t\t\tfloat: left;\n\t\t\t\tmargin-top: 10px;\n\t\t\t\ttext-align: center;\n\t\t\t\twidth: 33%;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 img {\n\t\t\t\tborder: 2px solid #cfcfcf;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-caption {\n\t\t\t\tmargin-left: 0;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t/* see gallery_shortcode() in wp-includes/media.php */\n\t\t</style>\n\t\t<div id='gallery-1' class='gallery galleryid-608421 galle